						<path style=" stroke:none;fill-rule:nonzero;fill:#ffffff;fill-opacity:1;" d="M 351.957031 77.582031 L 369.460938 77.582031 L 369.460938 193.285156 L 351.957031 193.285156 Z M 351.957031 77.582031 "/>
